<template>
    <v-network-graph
      class="graph"
      :nodes="nodeList"
      :edges="edgeList"
      :node-style="{ 'background-color': node.color }"
    />
  </template>
  
  <script>
  import { VNetworkGraph } from 'v-network-graph'
  
  export default {
    components: {
      VNetworkGraph
    },
    props: {
      nodeList: {
        type: Object,
        required: true
      },
      edgeList: {
        type: Object,
        required: true
      }
    },
    data() {
      return {
        nodes: this.nodeList,
        edges: this.edgeList
      }
    }
  }
  </script>
  
<style>
    .graph {
        width: 80vw;
        height: 60vh;
        border: 1px solid #fff;
        background-color: #8bbdd9;
    }
</style>
